{
    "version": 6,
    "bundle": "V2PSQDEIG2OSKW32KUTVYZBLYD6PIMA5",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "801017001",
    "title": "“皇帝”の激励",
    "enTitle": "The Emperor's Encouragement",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "<chrname>のレースが近づいてきた。\r\nこれまでに十分走り込んできたとは思う。\nだが、どうにも不安が拭えない……。",
            "enText": "<chrname>'s race is drawing<n>near. I'm\nsure we've done enough<n>running in preparation,\nbut I can't quite<n>shake off my anxieties...",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 123,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "pathId": 5624606437872487648,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "これで本当に勝てるのか？　調整はどうする？\r\n頭を悩ませていると――",
            "enText": "As I fret about whether our training has<n>been\nenough to win, a certain racer<n>happens by...",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "pathId": -8291436805985522160,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "難しい顔をしているな。\r\nどうかしたのか？",
            "enText": "That's quite a stern look on your face. Is<n>\nsomething the matter?",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "voiceIdx": 32,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "なんだか不安になってきて……",
                    "enText": "I'm just feeling nervous, that's all...",
                    "nextBlock": 4
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": -6863721965598118866
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 120,
                    "pathId": -7505279409868219358
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4945647320986146289,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "ふふっ。\r\nその心境自体は理解できる。",
            "enText": "Haha. I can deeply relate to that state of<n>mind.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 69,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": -388481343008246350
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 120,
                    "pathId": 1594558840424708820
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1961697402135940939,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "だが、動揺した姿はあまり見せない方がいい。\r\n彼女にまで不安を抱かせたくはないだろう。",
            "enText": "However, it would be best not to display<n>your\nunease so freely, lest it make your<n>trainee anxious\nas well.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 101,
            "voiceIdx": 49,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 121,
                    "pathId": 3288202444408559655
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": 4531714430355840677
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": -9176934735038028399
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -839325689210653041,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "率直に、君たちは自信を持っていいと思う。\r\n走り込みの量も質も、他の子に劣っていない。",
            "enText": "If you ask me, you two should have<n>confidence in\nyourselves. The number<n>and quality of your runs\nare second to<n>none.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 101,
            "voiceIdx": 38,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 3502509743081334511
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": 5131895017538309718
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 147,
                    "pathId": 7913574061110654774
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5673211069784131450,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "結果は自ずと出る。泰然自若として待つんだ。\r\n……なんて、言うは易し行うは難しだな。",
            "enText": "Good results will surely follow, so be<n>calm in your\nheart and rest assured. Of<n>course, I suppose this is\nmuch easier said<n>than done.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 99,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": 2902347179860888227
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": 6635088686653776981
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7566744777525467107,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "何か証を……そうだな、君が考えている\r\nレースに向けた調整メニューを聞かせてくれ。",
            "enText": "There must be more I can do to reassure<n>you...\nAh, I have just the idea. Tell me<n>how you are\npreparing for your race.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "voiceIdx": 37,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "レースに向けて軽めのスピード練習中心",
                    "enText": "We're focusing on moderate speed training.",
                    "nextBlock": 9
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "ハードな展開に備え、あえて重めの調整",
                    "enText": "We're training hard to prepare for the worst\ncase scenario.",
                    "nextBlock": 14
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": -5045768623896559569
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 87,
                    "pathId": -4610859403194148106
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3457162268108704798,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "体力を温存しスピード中心に、か。\r\nうん、やはりな。正攻法だ。理に適っている。",
            "enText": "Focusing on speed while preserving<n>energy... I\nsee. Yes, I expected as much.<n>That's an orthodox\nand logical approach.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "voiceIdx": 38,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": 3342250581559630649
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 158,
                    "pathId": -5175397579064568442
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4981948549285433279,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "確かに君の選んだ道はよく踏み馴らされた\r\n道だ。だからこそ不安に感じるのだろう。",
            "enText": "The path you have chosen is<n>well-traveled, which,\nI suppose, is<n>precisely why you feel so uneasy.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "voiceIdx": 79,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": 6266978835375410898
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": 4110672187608002665
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4609382423841706723,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "だがそれは、踏み外しさえしなければ\r\n栄光に繋がる帝道だと言える。",
            "enText": "But worry not. Staying on that path will<n>\nundoubtedly lead to glory.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": -5714415239325013015
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": 3055113492128834719
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 207,
                    "pathId": 8916471786136741128
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4897722511794457554,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "君たちにはそこを歩み続けられる強さがある。\r\n私はそう思っているよ。自信を持ちたまえ。",
            "enText": "I believe you two have the strength to<n>follow the\nroad you've chosen. There is<n>no need to doubt\nyourselves.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 101,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": 3353701891804186279
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": 8402548871448827051
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2725245736212259042,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "シンボリルドルフの言葉を聞いて\r\n少し不安も薄れ、自信を持つことができた。",
            "enText": "Symboli Rudolf's words ease my<n>anxieties a little,\nand I feel confidence<n>welling up within me once\nmore.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": -4034222326586509282
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": 9101627487564983750
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 818053882533067914,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "ふむ、なるほど。不安を払拭する意味でも、\r\nしっかり走っておきたいということか……。",
            "enText": "Hm, I see. So you're allaying those fears<n>of yours\nby training intensely and<n>preparing for any and all\npossibilities.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 99,
            "voiceIdx": 9,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": -6470488264824010708
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -6279009361868060455
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8788580927642004801,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "正攻法ではないかもしれないが……\r\n今の君たちには最適な調整だろう。",
            "enText": "Though it may not be the most orthodox<n>\napproach, I can see how it might be the<n>best one\nfor your current situation.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": -2034191342034982541
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": -8583691248877834985
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3558488752132327711,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "無我夢中で走る中で、憂いも迷いも躊躇いも\r\n全て振り切ってしまうことが期待できる。",
            "enText": "Once you lose yourself to the thrill of<n>the run, all\nyour fears, doubts, and<n>apprehensions will be left\nbehind in the<n>dust like forgotten sighs.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "voiceSheetId": "",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": -102886207155982309
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": -5064618624450111100
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 198,
                    "pathId": 8833043574334673150
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5135584756761424333,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "シンボリルドルフ",
            "enName": "Symboli Rudolf",
            "jpText": "うん、やはり君の選択は間違っていない。\r\n自信を持って彼女を導いてあげたまえ。",
            "enText": "Yes, I believe you have made the right<n>choice. Go\nforth and guide your racer<n>with confidence.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "voiceIdx": 38,
            "voiceSheetId": "051017001",
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
